name: よむ / y_o_m_y_o_m (Ganbare Douki-chan) Style LoRA
description:
This LoRA has been trained to look like よむ's artstyle. The goal of this LoRA is to be able to recreate the iconic characters and to imitate よむ's arstyle.

(you might know this artstyle from Ganbare Douki-chan)


This model has been trained on the SunshineMix＆SunlightMix checkpoint. link to the checkpoint here: https://civitai.com/models/9291/sunshinemixsunlightmix

(Other models seem to also work but it might be trial and error) :/

If you need to contact me, please write an email to: contact.kavzego@gmail.com

All credit goes to よむ, as all sample images that were used were from him.

Also note that if you use this LoRA to publish, sale, or post images online. Please Ask For Permission To The Artist (よむ)

I would really appreciate if you leave comments, suggestions, feedback, and more below. I'll be more than happy to read it! :)
